model.HuffmanCompression

Interface ICoder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Coder

    public interface ICoder
    Compression for level maps and solutions. Levels are compressed with Huffman compression algorithms. Solutions are compressed by an algorithm we developed.
    Author:
    Isan Rivkin and Daniel Hake.
